      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING TESFAY (7) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Last start placegetter over 520m at Q Parklands in a Grade 4/5 (30.03) but sharper journey suits this time. Has a strong winning record here at the trip including two wins. Makes plenty of appeal. EASTLY BLOOM (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (20.03) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Has ability and is one of the better chances. BOGIE PRIDE (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.04) at this track behind Star Assassin in a Grade 4/5. Expected to be in the finish again. PSIONIC PROWESS (3) scored with plenty to spare last time. Hard to beat again.",
